Class FileClackData

  • java.lang.Object
    • ClackData
      • data.FileClackData

  • public class FileClackData
extends ClackData
    The class creates a FileClackData that is a subclass of ClackData. Additionally, FileClackData has a filename represented by a string and the file's contents (fileContents) represented by a string.
